# MainLayout Component Usage

## Overview
`MainLayout` is a layout wrapper that composes `HeaderNav` and `Sidebar` and provides slots for main content and custom header/sidebar items.

## Import
If using via module federation, import from the remote entry:
```js
const MainLayout = await import('layoutMFE/MainLayout');
```

## Props
- `appLabel: string` — Application label
- `handleSearch?: Function` — Search callback
- `navMenuOptions?: Array<{ label, key, onClick?, icon?, text? }>` — Header menu options
- `handleNavMenuSelect?: Function` — Header menu select callback
- `userDisplayName: string` — User's display name
- `localizationLanguages?: Array<{ name, label, logo?, value }>` — Supported languages
- `selectedLanguage?: string` — Current language
- `handleLanguageChange?: Function` — Language change callback
- `menuItems: Array<{ label, key, onClick?, icon?, children?, condition? }>` — Sidebar menu items
- `ctaOptionsVertical?: Array<{ label, key, onClick?, icon?, text? }>` — Sidebar CTA options
- `enableCollapseMode?: boolean` — Enable sidebar collapse
- `isFixedExpandByDefault?: boolean` — Sidebar expanded by default
- `sidebarWidth?: string` — Sidebar width
- `enableMoreOptions?: boolean` — Enable sidebar pinning/more options
- `sidebarStorageKey?: string` — Local storage key for sidebar state
- `resetSearch?: boolean` — Reset search input

## Events
- `searchFocus` — Emitted when the search field is focused

## Slots
- `header-menu-items` — Custom content in the header
- `sidebar-footer` — Custom content in the sidebar footer
- Default slot — Main content area

## Example Usage
```vue
<MainLayout
  appLabel="My App"
  :handleSearch="onSearch"
  :navMenuOptions="navOptions"
  :handleNavMenuSelect="onMenuSelect"
  :userDisplayName="userName"
  :localizationLanguages="languages"
  :selectedLanguage="selectedLang"
  :handleLanguageChange="onLangChange"
  :menuItems="menuItems"
  :ctaOptionsVertical="ctaOptions"
  enableCollapseMode
  enableMoreOptions
  sidebarStorageKey="mySidebarKey"
>
  <template #header-menu-items>
    <!-- Custom header content -->
  </template>
  <template #sidebar-footer>
    <!-- Custom sidebar footer -->
  </template>
  <div>Main content here</div>
</MainLayout>
```

